# Info

Invoked when the server finishes loading (after all data packs are loaded).

# Available Event Fields

- `event.server` - The Minecraft server instance

# Example

```js
ServerEvents.loaded(event => {
	console.log('Server has loaded!')
	
	// Broadcast to all players (if any are already connected)
	event.server.tell('Server reloaded!')
})
```
